name: Asset Store Annihilation
description:
Asset Store Annihilation is a game made for the Dallas Society of Play's Cartridge Jam 3, which lasted 3 weeks. The original cartridge made for the jam is by Tyler Tomaseki. The game includes voice acting by Kyle Randal and features 54 different assets from the Unity asset store.

Inside the Unity asset store, assets of all kinds have been merging together and have gone aggressive, attacking anything and everything. You have been tasked with entering the asset store, putting the assets down, and solving this strange error that's going on.
